text:
Whitehall Street, south from Bowling Green, showing on the right, a side of the U.S. Custom House, and on the left the 8 story Kemble Building (No. 15-25). In the background appears the "El" structure at Battery Park.

March 13, 1938.

P. L. Sperr .
title: Manhattan: Whitehall Street - Bowling Green
